snippet.title: Breachers Clone Projector Update Reveal | VR Games Showcase Spring 2025
snippet.description:
Breachers is getting an awesome new gadget as part of a free update today. The Clone Projector allows players to place decoy versions of themselves around the map.

Buy Breachers on Quest, PS VR2, and PC VR: https://linktr.ee/BreachersVRGS

Experience heart-pounding, tactical multiplayer combat where strategy meets chaos. Choose your side—Enforcer or Revolter—and immerse yourself in thrilling close-quarters battles. With stunning environments and dynamic gameplay, Breachers™ promises endless excitement.
